reated\n AFTER INSERT ON auth.users\n FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION public.handle_new_user();\n\n-- Row Level Security (RLS) - dozvoli korisnicima da vide samo svoj red\nALTER TABLE users ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;\n\n-- Policy: Korisnici mogu čitati samo svoje podatke\nCREATE POLICY \"Users can view own profile\"\n ON users FOR SELECT\n USING (auth.uid() = id);\n\n-- Policy: Korisnici mogu ažurirati samo svoje podatke\nCREATE POLICY \"Users can update own profile\"\n ON users FOR UPDATE\n USING (auth.uid() = id);\n```\n\n## 4. Email Validacija u Supabase\n\nDa biste osigurali da samo **@fsre.sum.ba** emailovi mogu biti registrovani:\n\n### Opcija 1: Constraint u bazi podataka\n\n```sql\n-- Dodaj constraint za email domenu\nALTER TABLE auth.users\nADD CONSTRAINT email_domain_check\nCHECK (email LIKE '%@fsre.sum.ba');\n```\n\n### Opcija 2: Database Function za validaciju\n\n```sql\nCREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION validate_email_domain()\nRETURNS TRIGGER AS $$\nBEGIN\n IF NEW.email NOT LIKE '%@fsre.sum.ba' THEN\n RAISE EXCEPTION 'Email mora biti sa domene @fsre.sum.ba';\n END IF;\n RETURN NEW;\nEND;\n$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;\n\nCREATE TRIGGER validate_email_before_insert\n BEFORE INSERT ON auth.users\n FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION validate_email_domain();\n```\n\n## 5. Testiranje\n\n### Test Podaci\n\nMožete kreirati test korisnike putem Supabase Authentication dashboard ili SQL:\n\n```sql\n-- Napomena: Za kreiranje auth users, najbolje je koristiti Supabase Auth API ili Dashboard\n-- Evo primjera insert-a u users tabelu nakon što je auth user kreiran:\n\nINSERT INTO users (id, email, full_name, role) VALUES\n('uuid-ovdje', 'student1@fsre.sum.ba', 'Marko Marković', 'student'),\n('uuid-ovdje', 'profesor1@fsre.sum.ba', 'Dr. Ana Anić', 'profesor');\n```\n\n## 6. Email Settings (Opciono)\n\nAko želite da korisnici potvrde email:\n\n1. Idite na **Authentication > Settings** u Supabase Dashboard\n2. Omogućite **Email Confirmations**\n3. Konfigurirajte SMTP settings za slanje emailo