ati Google, GitHub login kroz Supabase Dashboard.\n"}"}}]},{"role":"tool","name":"write","tool_call_id":"toolu_01NrnGzsfHCTroWzWZEggL7Z","content":"Wrote contents to C:/Users/nikol/AndroidStudioProjects/attendance-app/SUPABASE_SETUP.md.

