ite korisnika\n3. Kliknite \"...\" menu → Send confirmation email\n4. Ili manually potvrdite: \"...\" → Confirm email\n\n**Za development:**\n- Disable email confirmation:\n - Dashboard → Authentication → Settings → Enable email confirmations (OFF)\n\n---\n\n## Runtime Errors\n\n### 14. NetworkOnMainThreadException\n\n**Greška:**\n```\nandroid.os.NetworkOnMainThreadException\n```\n\n**Uzrok:** Network pozivi se izvršavaju na Main/UI thread-u.\n\n**Rješenje:**\n- Već implementirano u `SupabaseClient.java` sa `ExecutorService`\n- Ako dodajete nove network pozive, koristite:\n\n```java\nExecutorService executor = Executors.newSingleThreadExecutor();\nexecutor.execute(() -> {\n // Network call ovdje\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n### 15. JSON Parsing Error\n\n**Greška:**\n```\norg.json.JSONException: Value cannot be converted\n```\n\n**Rješenje:**\n1. Provjerite response format iz Supabase-a\n2. Provjerite da tabela vraća očekivane kolone\n3. Use Logcat za debug:\n\n```java\nLog.d(\"SupabaseClient\", \"Response: \" + response.toString());\n```\n\n---\n\n## Android Studio Issues\n\n### 16. Android Studio Freezes\n\n**Rješenje:**\n1. File → Invalidate Caches / Restart\n2. Povećajte heap size:\n - Help → Edit Custom VM Options\n - Dodajte: `-Xmx4096m`\n\n---\n\n### 17. Gradle Daemon Issues\n\n**Greška:**\n```\nGradle daemon disappeared unexpectedly\n```\n\n**Rješenje:**\n```bash\n# Stopirajte sve Gradle daemon procese:\n./gradlew --stop\n\n# Ili u Windows:\ngradlew.bat --stop\n\n# Zatim rebuild:\n./gradlew clean build\n```\n\n---\n\n## Security Issues\n\n### 18. Credentials Exposed in Git\n\n**Problem:** Slučajno ste commit-ovali Supabase kredencijale.\n\n**Rješenje:**\n\n```bash\n# 1. Uklonite fajl iz Git history:\ngit filter-branch --force --index-filter \\\n \"git rm --cached --ignore-unmatch app/src/main/java/com/example/studentqrscanner/config/SupabaseClient.java\" \\\n --prune-empty --tag-name-filter cat -- --all\n\n# 2. Force push:\ngit push origin --force --all\n\n# 3. Rotira