_user_created\n AFTER INSERT ON auth.users\n FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION public.handle_new_user();\n\n-- Row Level Security (RLS) - dozvoli korisnicima da vide samo svoj red\nALTER TABLE users ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;\n\n-- Policy: Korisnici mogu čitati samo svoje podatke\nCREATE POLICY \"Users can view own profile\"\n ON users FOR SELECT\n USING (auth.uid() = id);\n\n-- Policy: Korisnici mogu ažurirati samo svoje podatke\nCREATE POLICY \"Users can update own profile\"\n ON users FOR UPDATE\n USING (auth.uid() = id);\n```\n\n## 4. Email Validacija u Supabase (Opciono)\n\nDa biste osigurali da samo **@fsre.sum.ba** emailovi mogu biti dodati:\n\n### Database Function za validaciju\n\n```sql\nCREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION validate_email_domain()\nRETURNS TRIGGER AS $$\nBEGIN\n IF NEW.email NOT LIKE '%@fsre.sum.ba' THEN\n RAISE EXCEPTION 'Email mora biti sa domene @fsre.sum.ba';\n END IF;\n RETURN NEW;\nEND;\n$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql;\n\nCREATE TRIGGER validate_email_before_insert\n BEFORE INSERT ON auth.users\n FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION validate_email_domain();\n```\n\n**Napomena:** Client-side validacija je već implementirana u aplikaciji.\n\n## 5. Dodavanje Korisnika\n\n### Korisnici se dodaju RUČNO u Supabase Dashboard\n\n**Korak po korak:**\n\n1. Idite na **Authentication** → **Users**\n2. Kliknite **Add user**\n3. Popunite polja:\n - **Email:** mora biti `@fsre.sum.ba` (npr. `student1@fsre.sum.ba`)\n - **Password:** minimum 6 karaktera\n - **Auto Confirm User:** ✅ **OBAVEZNO OZNAČITE**\n4. Kliknite **Create user**\n\n### Dodavanje Metadata (Role i Full Name)\n\nNakon što je korisnik kreiran:\n\n1. U **Users** listi, kliknite na email korisnika\n2. Skrolujte do **Raw user meta data**\n3. Dodajte JSON:\n\n**Za studenta:**\n```json\n{\n \"full_name\": \"Marko Marković\",\n \"role\": \"student\"\n}\n```\n\n**Za profesora:**\n```json\n{\n \"full_name\": \"Dr. Ana Anić\",\n \"role\": \"profesor\"\n}\n```\n\n4. Kliknite **Save**\n\n**VAŽNO:** Trigger `on_auth_user_created` će automatski kreirati profil u `users` tabeli kada dodate metadata.\n\n### Primjer Test Korisnika\n\n```\nStudent:\n- Email: test.student@fsre.sum.ba\n- Password: test123456\n- Metadata: { \"full_name\": \"Test Student\", \"role\": \"student\" }\n\nProfesor:\n- Email: test.profesor@fsre.sum.ba \n- Password: test123456\n- Metadata: { \"full_name\": \"Test Profesor\", \"role\": \"profesor\" }\n```\n\n## 6. Verifikacija Setup-a\n\n### Provjerite Trigger\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM pg_trigger WHERE tgname = 'on_auth_user_created';\n```\n\nTrebali biste vidjeti jedan red sa triggerom.\n\n### Provjerite Users Tabelu\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM users;\n```\n\nNakon što dodate korisnike u Authentication, ovdje bi trebali biti vidljivi njihovi profili.\n\n### Provjerite RLS Policies\n\n```sql\nSELECT * FROM pg_policies WHERE tablename = 'users';\n```\n\nTrebali biste vidjeti 2 policy-a (view i update).\n\n## 7. Email Settings (Opciono)\n\nAko želite da Supabase šalje confirmation emailove:\n\n1. Idite na **Authentication** → **Settings**\n2. **Enable Email Confirmations** (opciono - za development možete ostaviti OFF)\n3. **Konfiguriši SMTP** settings za slanje emailova (opciono)\n\n**Za development:** Preporučujemo da **ostavite email confirmation OFF** i koristite \"Auto Confirm User\" pri kreiranju korisnika.\n\n## 8. Security Best Practices\n\n### Environment Variables\n\nUmjesto hardcoding kredencijala u kod, preporučuje se:\n\n1. Kreirajte `local.properties` fajl (već je u `.gitignore`):\n```properties\nsupabase.url=https://YOUR_PROJECT_ID.supabase.co\nsupabase.anon.key=YOUR_ANON_KEY\n```\n\n2. Učitajte ih u `app/build.gradle`:\n```gradle\nandroid {\n defaultConfig {\n Properties properties = new Properties()\n properties.load(project.rootProject.file('local.properties').newDataInputStream())\n \n buildConfigField \"String\", \"SUPABASE_URL\", \"\\\"${properties.getProperty('supabase.url')}\\\"\"\n buildConfigField \"String\", \"SUPABASE_ANON_KEY\", \"\\\"${properties.getProperty('supabase.anon.key')}\\\"\"\n }\n \n buildFeatures {\n buildConfig = true\n }\n}\n```\n\n3. Koristite ih u kodu:\n```java\nprivate static final String SUPABASE_URL = BuildConfig.SUPABASE_URL;\nprivate static final String SUPABASE_ANON_KEY = BuildConfig.SUPABASE_ANON_KEY;\n```\n\n## 9. Troubleshooting\n\n### Greška: \"Invalid API Key\"\n- Provjerite da ste ispravno kopirali `SUPABASE_ANON_KEY`\n- Koristite **anon/public** key, ne **service_role** key\n\n### Greška: \"User profil nije pronađen\"\n- Provjerite da li je trigger `on_auth_user_created` pravilno kreiran\n- Provjerite da li ste dodali metadata (full_name i role)\n- Provjerite RLS policies\n\n### Greška: \"Email not confirmed\"\n- Označite **Auto Confirm User** pri kreiranju\n- Ili ručno potvrdite: Users → ... menu → Confirm email\n\n### Greška pri konekciji\n- Provjerite internet konekciju\n- Provjerite da ste dodali Internet permission u AndroidManifest.xml\n\n## 10. SQL Skripta - Kompletan Setup\n\nEvo kompletne SQL skripte koju možete copy-paste:\n\n```sql\n-- 1. ENUM za role\nCREATE TYPE user_role AS ENUM ('student', 'profesor');\n\n-- 2. Users tabela\nCREATE TABLE users (\n id UUID PRIMARY KEY REFERENCES auth.users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,\n email TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,\n full_name TEXT NOT NULL,\n role user_role NOT NULL DEFAULT 'student',\n created_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT NOW(),\n updated_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT NOW()\n);\n\n-- 3. Trigger funkcija\nCREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION public.handle_new_user()\nRETURNS TRIGGER AS $$\nBEGIN\n INSERT INTO public.users (id, email, full_name, role)\n VALUES (\n NEW.id,\n NEW.email,\n COALESCE(NEW.raw_user_meta_data->>'full_name', ''),\n COALESCE((NEW.raw_user_meta_data->>'role')::user_role, 'student')\n );\n RETURN NEW;\nEND;\n$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql SECURITY DEFINER;\n\n-- 4. Trigger\nCREATE TRIGGER on_auth_user_created\n AFTER INSERT ON auth.users\n FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION public.handle_new_user();\n\n-- 5. RLS\nALTER TABLE users 