## Rješenje - Kreiranje Database Schema

### Korak 1: Otvorite Supabase SQL Editor

1. Idite na https://supabase.com
2. Otvorite vaš projekat
3. Lijeva strana → **SQL Editor**
4. Kliknite **New query**

### Korak 2: Izvršite Ovu SQL Skriptu

Copy-paste **CIJELU** skriptu ispod i kliknite **RUN**:

```sql
-- 1. Kreiranje ENUM tipa za user roles
CREATE TYPE user_role AS ENUM ('student', 'profesor');

-- 2. Kreiranje users tabele
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS users (
 id UUID PRIMARY KEY REFERENCES auth.users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
 email TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,
 full_name TEXT NOT NULL,
 role user_role NOT NULL DEFAULT 'student',
 created_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT NOW(),
 updated_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE DEFAULT NOW()
);

-- 3. Trigger funkcija za automatsko popunjavanje
CREATE OR REPLACE FUNCTION public.handle_new_user()
RETURNS TRIGGER AS $$
BEGIN
 INSERT INTO public.users (id, email, full_name, role)
 VALUES (
 NEW.id,
 NEW.email,
 COALESCE(NEW.raw_user_meta_data->>'full_name', 'User'),
 COALESCE((NEW.raw_user_meta_data->>'role')::user_role, 'student')
 );
 RETURN NEW;
END;
$$ LANGUAGE plpgsql SECURITY DEFINER;

-- 4. Kreiranje triggera
DROP TRIGGER IF EXISTS on_auth_user_created ON auth.users;
CREATE TRIGGER on_auth_user_created
 AFTER INSERT ON auth.users
 FOR EACH ROW EXECUTE FUNCTION public.handle_new_user();

-- 5. Row Level Security
ALTER TABLE users ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;

-- 6. Obriši stare policies ako postoje
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Users can view own profile" ON users;
DROP POLICY IF EXISTS "Users can update own profile" ON users;

-- 7. Kreiraj nove policies
CREATE POLICY "Users can view own profile"
 ON users FOR SELECT
 USING (auth.uid() = id);

CREATE POLICY "Users can update own profile"
 ON users FOR UPDATE
 USING (auth.uid() = id);
```

### Korak 3: Verifikuj da je Sve Kreirano

U Supabase SQL Editor, izvršite ovu provjeru:

```sql
-- Provjeri da li tabela postoji
SELECT * FROM users;

-- Provjeri da li trigger postoji
SELECT * FROM pg_trigger WHERE tgname = 'on_auth_user_created';
```

Ako vam vrati rezultate (čak i prazne), sve je OK!

